text: Yevhen Bohonosiuk (born 18 January 1982) is a Ukrainian gymnast. He competed in six events at the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Ukraine Category:Gymnasts at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Kyiv
